==Going to Entrana==
===Trying to place the orb on the altar===
* {{tbox|You should probably put that in a pouch or it might get damaged!}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Placing the pouch on the altar===
* {{qact|Tthe screen fades to black as a cutscene begins. Three monks carrying a relic can be seen walking into the church.}}
* {{qact|As the monks approach the altar, the assassin teleports in, wielding the bow-sword, and kills one of the monks.}}
* '''High Priest:''' {{overhead|Protect the relic!}}
* {{qact|The monk carrying the relic tries to flee, but the assassin kills him with an arrow.}}
* '''Monk:''' {{overhead|You won't have it!}}
* {{qact|The last monk approaches the assassin and hits him with a staff, attempting to stop him from claiming it, but the assassin cuts the monk down.}}
* {{qact|As the assassin picks up the relic and teleports away, the pouch containing the orb on the altar explodes, and the High Priest shields himself from the explosion.}}
* {{qact|The screen fades to black as the cutscene ends.}}

===The Surprise===
* '''High Priest:''' The relic! This is a disaster!
* '''High Priest:''' Adventurer, did you see who put that teleport beacon on the altar?
* '''Player:''' Uh... yeah, about that...
* '''High Priest:''' What is it?
* '''Player:''' I put it there...
* '''High Priest:''' What? Why?
* '''Player:''' There was this monk near Paterdomus. He told me it was a gift...
* '''High Priest:''' No worshipper of Saradomin would ever do something like this! Adventurer, you must return to Paterdomus and see if you can find any trace of this 'monk'.
* '''Player:''' I'll go right away.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the High Priest again===
* '''High Priest:''' Adventurer, have you found that 'monk' yet?
* '''Player:''' Not yet.
* '''High Priest:''' Please hurry to Paterdomus and see if you can find any trace of him.
* {{tact|end}}

==Investigating the Surprise==
===Finding the dead monk===
* {{tbox|The poor guy appears to have been killed by powerful magic!}}
* '''Player:''' This isn't good. I'd better get back and tell the High Priest.
* {{tact|end}}

===Returning to the High Priest in Entrana===
* '''High Priest:''' Adventurer, have you found that 'monk' yet?
* '''Player:''' I went back to Paterdomus, but all I found was a dead body.
* '''High Priest:''' What?
* '''Player:''' It looked like he'd been killed by magic. The thing is, I'm not convinced he was the person I spoke to before.
* '''High Priest:''' This is not good. That relic wasn't just for show! It was once part of a powerful artefact. You must report this to Sir Tiffy Cashien in Falador Park.
* '''Player:''' I'll head there right away.
* {{tact|end}}

==Wrapping Up==
===Reporting to Sir Tiffy===
* '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' Jolly good show on getting into the White Knights, what?
* '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' Now how can I help you old [boy/girl/bean]?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Devious Minds.}}
** '''Player:''' I've got some bad news...
** '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' This wouldn't be about that old relic being stolen from Entrana, would it?
** '''Player:''' Uh... yeah, how'd you know?
** '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' Part of the business, old bean. So what do you know about what went on?
** '''Player:''' Well there was this monk who needed help...
** {{tbox|You explain everything that happened.}}
** '''Player:''' ... and so I was told to come see you.
** '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' Good, that confirms our own intel. We will get to work at once.
** '''Player:''' Is there anything I can do to help?
** '''Sir Tiffy Cashien:''' Not yet, but we'll be in touch if we need you, old bean. For now, you should be on your way, but don't worry, we'll get to the bottom of this!
** {{Qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Something else.}}

{{Devious Minds}}
